title: Meek Mill Rips Wale: “He Not MMG IM MAKING THAT CALL – Tryna Call Me Saying Rozay Owe Us Money”
text: Meek Mill Rips Wale: “He Not MMG IM MAKING THAT CALL – Tryna Call Me Saying Rozay Owe Us Money” Wednesday, 21 October 2015 (5 minutes ago) Maybach Music Group’s Meek Mill has stepped forward to speak out on estranged labelmate Wale name-dropping him in a new radio interview this week. Meek blasted Wale on Instagram Wednesday (October 21) night. Check out what Wale said in his interview on the next page… The post Meek Mill Rips Wale: “He Not MMG IM MAKING THAT CALL – Tryna Call Me Saying Rozay Owe Us Money” appeared first on For The Best In Hip-Hop News - SOHH.com.
